[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0501","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0773","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 lpset 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 的 /usr/bin/lpset 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序提交特制的参数或环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存空间，从而获取 root 权限，完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需具有本地登录权限，无需网络访问即可完成提权利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0773"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.700","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 106980（Solaris 7 适用），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod 555 /usr/bin/lpset` 移除 setuid 位，限制本地普通用户以提权方式运行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.netspace.org/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind9905B&L=bugtraq&P=R2017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19206"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0723","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 CSRSS 工作线程耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的客户端服务器运行时子系统（CSRSS）存在工作线程耗尽漏洞。当 CSRSS 的所有工作线程均处于等待用户输入状态时，远程攻击者可通过发送大量恶意请求消耗系统可用线程资源，导致 CSRSS 无法处理新的合法请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，造成系统服务不可用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0723"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.320","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的安全更新 (MS99-032)，此更新限制了 CSRSS 工作线程的数量并解决了线程耗尽问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233323","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/478","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-021"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0499","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0772","title":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 及 Survey Utility 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 2301 端口发送超长字符串，触发服务组件缓冲区溢出，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Compaq 多款服务器管理软件，危害等级中危，CVSS 评分 6.4。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0772"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.590","remediation":"建议升级至 Compaq 官方修补版本（Insight Management Agents 5.0 及以上版本）以修复长字符串导致的服务崩溃漏洞。如无法升级，可在防火墙策略中限制 TCP 2301 端口的访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理站 IP 连接。若业务不需要该服务，建议直接禁用 Compaq Insight Management Agent 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0772"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0497","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0300","title":"Sun Solaris NIS+ nis_cachemgr 安全绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 缓存管理器存在安全设计缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向缓存中注入恶意的 NIS+ 服务器信息。当客户端查询网络信息服务时，将连接到攻击者控制的伪造服务器，导致敏感信息（如用户凭据、主机配置）被窃取或服务遭到劫持。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0300"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.247","remediation":"针对 Solaris NIS+ 的 nis_cachemgr 漏洞，建议立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #155 中提供的官方补丁。如运行 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 且无法打补丁，应在网络边界通过防火墙限制对 nis_cachemgr 端口（TCP/UDP 387）的访问，仅允许受信 NIS+ 服务器通信。由于 NIS+ 已停止维护，建议迁移至基于 LDAP 的命名服务以获得长期安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/155","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0300","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0300.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0300.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--12792e2d-cd40-4418-b42c-679d4e4e14e3.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0497.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0496","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0771","title":"Compaq Management Agents 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Compaq Management Agents 及 Survey Utility 的 Web 组件存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 Web 界面发送包含 `../` 序列的特制 HTTP 请求，突破路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，如系统配置文件或敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Compaq Client Management Agents 3.70/4.0、Insight Management Agents 4.21 A/4.22 A/4.30 A、Survey Utility 2.0 等多个版本。攻击者利用该漏洞可获取服务器敏感信息，为后续攻击提供跳板。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0771"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.453","remediation":"升级至 Compaq 官方修复版本（该漏洞在后续 Management Agents 版本中已修复，Compaq 后被 HP 收购，对应产品线演进为 HP Insight Management Agents）。如无法升级，可采取以下缓解措施：在防火墙上限制仅信任 IP 能访问管理代理的 Web 端口（默认 2301）；若不需要 Web 管理功能，可禁用 Web 服务器组件或移除 www 目录下的可执行脚本，以阻断路径遍历攻击路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0771","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19225"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0495","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0299","title":"FreeBSD lpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 的 lpd（行式打印机守护进程）在处理超长 DNS 主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的打印服务发送特制的主机名数据触发该溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0299"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.117","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至已修复该漏洞的版本（4.0 及以上）。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 lpd 行并重启 inetd 以禁用打印机守护进程；若需继续使用 lpd，在 /etc/hosts.lpd 和白名单中限制允许访问的客户端 IP，并在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 515 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0299","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0299.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/lpd_freebsd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0299.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83077/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0495.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0494","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0298","title":"SunOS ypbind 路径遍历文件覆盖漏洞","description":"SunOS 与 Linux Slackware 系统中 ypbind 服务在启用 -ypset 或 -ypsetme 选项时存在路径遍历漏洞。远程或本地攻击者可通过构造包含 ..（点点）的特殊请求，绕过目录限制覆盖系统任意文件，导致权限提升或服务异常。该漏洞影响运行 ypbind 且开启上述选项的 SunOS 及 Slackware 系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0298"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-02-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.990","remediation":"禁止使用 -ypset 和 -ypsetme 参数启动 ypbind，仅允许通过 ypserv 配置文件（/var/yp/securenets）确定的受信 NIS 服务器绑定。在防火墙层面限制 UDP 端口 111 和 32770-32800 的外部访问，或禁用 NIS 改用 LDAP 认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/06_ypbindsetme_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0298","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0298.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1441/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0298.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000146.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0494.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0493","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0493.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0297","title":"Vixie Cron 库缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 库 3.0 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响的 cron 守护进程提交特制的超长环境变量，触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖返回地址并劫持程序执行流。成功利用此漏洞可获得目标系统的 root 权限，完全控制主机。该漏洞影响 Vixie Cron 3.0 及之前版本，需具有本地访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0297"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.877","remediation":"立即升级 Vixie Cron 至 3.0pl1 或更高版本，该版本已修复环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞。现代 Linux 发行版应确保使用 cronie 替代（如安装 cronie 包），或通过系统包管理器更新 cron 至最新版本。临时缓解措施包括限制不可信用户的本地登录访问，以及使用 SELinux/AppArmor 限制 cron 守护进程的权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0297"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0493.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0492","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0770","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 非SYN连接超时拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 存在拒绝服务漏洞。该防火墙对以 ACK 等非 SYN 数据包开始的连接设置了过长的超时时间，远程攻击者可通过向无法响应的目标系统发送大量此类连接请求，耗尽防火墙会话表资源，导致无法处理正常连接请求。该漏洞影响 Firewall-1 3.0 及 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0770"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.327","remediation":"升级 Check Point Firewall-1 至 4.1 及以上版本，该版本修复了非 SYN 包长超时问题，引入了正确的 TCP 状态跟踪机制。如无法升级，可在防火墙上手动调低非 SYN 连接的超时阈值，并限制单源 IP 的并发连接数，同时部署 ingress 过滤以阻断伪造源地址的攻击流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1027","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19436"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0489","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0769","title":"ISC Vixie Cron MAILTO 环境变量本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在参数注入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置特制的 MAILTO 环境变量向 sendmail 命令传递恶意参数，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenLinux 2.2、Debian 2.1/2.2、RedHat 6.0 等 Linux 发行版，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0769"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.193","remediation":"Red Hat 6.0 用户升级 cron 包至 3.0pl1-24 及以上版本（RHSA-1999:023）；Debian 2.1/2.2 用户升级 cron 包至 3.0pl1-47 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 2.2 用户应用厂商发布的 cron 安全补丁。升级后 cron 将 MAILTO 值仅作为收件地址处理，不再允许传递额外参数给 sendmail。如无法升级，可移除 crontab 中不受信任用户的 MAILTO 设置或限制 cron 的使用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19474"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0487","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0293","title":"Cisco IOS AAA认证远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 系统的 AAA（认证、授权、审计）认证模块存在授权绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可在未获得合法凭据的情况下绕过认证机制，直接执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多款 Cisco 路由器及交换机设备，攻击者利用该漏洞可完全控制目标设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。目前建议用户升级至修复版本或配置严格的访问控制列表进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0293"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.380","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复该漏洞的版本（如 11.x 及以上已打补丁版本），启用 `aaa new-model` 并配置 TACACS+ 或 RADIUS 服务器进行认证授权，避免仅依赖本地 enable 密码。在 `aaa authentication` 和 `aaa authorization` 命令中指定 `group tacacs+` 作为首选方法，禁止未认证用户通过 AAA 接口执行命令。如无法升级，在受控接口上配置 ACL 限制仅允许可信管理源 IP 访问设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2007/CVE-2007-4632.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82266/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0486","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0292","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Winpopup 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 Winpopup（信使服务）在处理用户名字段时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含超长用户名的弹出消息触发该漏洞，导致目标系统耗尽系统资源或信使服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。Microsoft 官方未发布针对此漏洞的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0292"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.240","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 Winpopup 消息处理中的缓冲区问题。如系统已不受支持，建议立即升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本，或在防火墙和本地安全策略中禁用 Messenger 服务（net stop messenger）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0292","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0292.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5/GHSA-5hp9-m282-4fm5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0292.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d5e467d6-9db2-4f83-aa80-400388f5bd0e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0486.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0485","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0291","title":"Qbik WinGate 代理默认无密码未授权访问漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器在默认安装时未设置访问密码，导致缺乏必要的身份认证机制。远程攻击者可在无需任何认证的条件下连接至该代理服务，利用其开放的代理功能转发网络连接请求，从而隐藏攻击来源、绕过访问控制或发起匿名攻击。该漏洞影响 WinGate 全系列早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0291"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.093","remediation":"立即为 WinGate 代理服务设置管理密码并启用用户认证机制；在 GateKeeper 管理控制台中配置访问控制列表，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址段使用代理服务；如业务不需要代理功能，直接卸载或禁用 WinGate 服务；同时在网络防火墙层面拦截外部对 8080/1080 等常见代理端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wingate.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0484","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0290","title":"Qbik WinGate Telnet Proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate Telnet 代理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者通过向目标系统的 Telnet 代理端口发起大量本地主机连接请求，可耗尽代理服务资源导致服务崩溃，无法正常处理后续合法连接。该漏洞影响 Qbik WinGate 的 Telnet 代理模块，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，风险等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0290"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.970","remediation":"建议升级 WinGate 至 4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续迭代中修复。如无法升级，可在 WinGate 网关属性中禁用 telnet 代理服务（取消 Telnet Proxy 复选框），或在防火墙上限制对 telnet 代理端口（默认 23）的入站连接数量，仅允许可信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wingate_denial.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0483","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0768","title":"红帽 (Red Hat) 和 SUSE Linux Vixie Cron 服务 MAILTO 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 MAILTO 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 及 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.0/6.1 等系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制 cron 任务的 MAILTO 变量长度。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0768"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.067","remediation":"立即升级 vixie-cron 至 3.0.1-56 及以上版本（Red Hat）或安装 SUSE 对应安全补丁；若无法升级，在 crontab 中避免使用 MAILTO 变量或限制 MAILTO 值长度不超过 256 字节；建议迁移至现代 Linux 发行版（如 RHEL 8+），其 cronie 已内置该漏洞修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/602","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19470"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml"}]